con:config.con:query: SELECT distinct m.WGP_ID_NBR,m.RECORD_KEY,m.WGP_TTL_ACTL_WGT,m.WGP_PLANNED_DEST_ORZ_ZN_CD,m.WGP_TTL_NBR_HNDLNG_UNITS from Legacy.M204_WGP m where WGP_ID_NBR = '${SpreadSheet#PRO}' order by m.WGP_ID_NBR desc

select distinct s.PRO_NB ,s.Shipment_Key,s.WGP_Record_key ,s.Total_Actual_Weight_QT,s.Planned_Dest_Fclty_Rtg_Zone_CD , s.Total_Handling_Units_QT from Legacy.M204_WGP m where WGP_ID_NBR = '${SpreadSheet#PRO}' order by m.WGP_ID_NBR desc
